Author: Sven Joachim <svenjoac@gmx.de>
Description: Remove xterm+focus from alacritty terminfo entry
 Vim versions before 9.0.1619 misbehave with TERM=alacritty when
 switching focus to or from the terminal window.  Disable support for
 these events until a fixed version of Vim is in Denbian testing.
Bug: https://github.com/vim/vim/issues/12499
Bug-Debian: https://bugs.debian.org/1038401
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2023-06-28

--- ncurses-6.4+20230625.orig/misc/terminfo.src
+++ ncurses-6.4+20230625/misc/terminfo.src
@@ -7791,7 +7791,7 @@ alacritty+common|base fragment for alacr
 	use=xterm-basic, use=xterm+app, use=ansi+rep,
 	use=xterm+tmux, use=ecma+strikeout, use=xterm+sl-twm,
 	use=ecma+italics, use=xterm+pce2, use=xterm+pcc2,
-	use=xterm+pcf2, use=bracketed+paste, use=xterm+focus,
+	use=xterm+pcf2, use=bracketed+paste,
 
